Preconditions:
- The input array `nums` is not null.
- The length of the input array `nums` is at least 1 and at most 10^5.
- Each element in the input array `nums` is an integer.
- Each element in the input array `nums` is within the range of -10^9 to 10^9.

Postconditions:
- The return value is an integer.
- The return value represents the minimum difference between the largest and smallest value of `nums` after performing at most three moves.